            <div class="member_about">
              <p>Minister Michael Oyelere is an academic with over 15 years of teaching experience in United Kingdom higher institutions. He is a member of British Universities Industrial Relations Association (BUIRA). He is also an academic member of the Chartered Institute of Personnel and Development (CIPD) and a Fellow of the Higher Education Academy (HEA).</p>

              <p>Michael has been an active member of the Open Heaven Christian Centre Edgware for over ten years and has been part of the prayer team for over seven years. He is currently responsible for coordinating the activities of the prayer team.</p>

              <p>He is passionate about prayers and has been involved in organising prayer and bible study meeting in all the organisations he worked with. He is also interested in sports and loves to cycle. He is married to Tope Oyelere and is blessed with children.</p>
